{% extends "_base.html.j2" %}
{% block title %}{{ seo.title }}{% endblock %}
{% block meta_description %}{{ seo.description }}{% endblock %}
{% block canonical %}<link rel="canonical" href="{{ seo.canonical }}">{% endblock %}
{% block og_tags %}
<meta property="og:title" content="{{ seo.title | e }}">
<meta property="og:description" content="{{ seo.description | e }}">
<meta property="og:url" content="{{ seo.canonical }}">
{% endblock %}

{% block content %}
<section class="hero" style="padding:2.5rem 0 2rem;">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Sources &amp; Methodology</h1>
    <p>Where our news comes from and how we decide what to cover.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<main class="container" style="max-width:760px;margin:2rem auto;padding:0 1.25rem;">

  <h2>Primary Sources</h2>
  <p>Every briefing is based on reporting or official announcements from at least one of the following:</p>

  <ul style="line-height:1.9;">
    <li><strong>VA.gov News</strong> — official press releases from the Department of Veterans Affairs</li>
    <li><strong>DoD News</strong> — Department of Defense announcements, including pay and policy changes</li>
    <li><strong>Federal Register</strong> — official rules and proposed rules from VA, DoD, and OPM</li>
    <li><strong>Congress.gov / GovTrack</strong> — legislation introduced or passed by the House and Senate Veterans' Affairs committees</li>
    <li><strong>DFAS</strong> — Defense Finance and Accounting Service military pay tables</li>
    <li><strong>DoD BAH Rates</strong> — Basic Allowance for Housing rate tables by location and pay grade</li>
    <li><strong>Google News</strong> — curated headlines from credentialed outlets (Military Times, Stars and Stripes, Defense.gov, Military.com, Task &amp; Purpose, and others)</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 style="margin-top:2rem;">How We Select Stories</h2>
  <p>Our automated pipeline scores each article for relevance to veterans and military families. We use the following criteria:</p>
  <ul style="line-height:1.9;">
    <li>Direct impact on VA disability ratings or COLA adjustments</li>
    <li>Changes to military retirement or Blended Retirement System rules</li>
    <li>PACT Act / burn-pit policy updates</li>
    <li>Government shutdown risk or federal pay freezes affecting veterans</li>
    <li>New legislation passing committee or the full House/Senate</li>
  </ul>
  <p>We set a <strong>minimum relevance threshold of 4/10</strong>. Stories scoring below that are discarded.</p>

  <h2 style="margin-top:2rem;">Editorial Independence</h2>
  <p>Rank and Pay is independent and not affiliated with the Department of Veterans Affairs, DoD, or any VSO. We do not accept sponsored content that influences our editorial coverage.</p>

  <h2 style="margin-top:2rem;">Disclaimer</h2>
  <div class="page-disclaimer" style="margin-top:0.75rem;">
    Content on this site is for informational purposes only. It does not constitute legal, financial, or benefits advice. Always verify information with the VA, a VSO, or an accredited claims agent before making decisions about your benefits.
  </div>

  <p style="margin-top:2rem;font-size:0.875rem;"><a href="/">&larr; Home</a></p>
</main>
{% endblock %}
